Sandip is your friend and your guest.

01:30:17.681 --> 01:30:20.081
Everybody knows that.

01:30:20.450 --> 01:30:24.819
Soon they'll believe whatever he does
is done with your sanction.

01:30:25.655 --> 01:30:30.957
