l kept everything.

01:37:03.920 --> 01:37:05.444
Have you ever used it?

01:37:08.891 --> 01:37:13.453
lt's no good for anything,
not even for washing clothes.

01:37:19.569 --> 01:37:22.163
What foolish notions l had back then.

01:37:22.271 --> 01:37:23.966
