01:53:59.802 --> 01:54:01.292
Money?

01:54:01.804 --> 01:54:05.331
So little? There can't be
more than 500 in those bags.

01:54:05.975 --> 01:54:09.342
You must have forgotten.
l asked for 5,000 rupees.

01:54:15.151 --> 01:54:16.743
What's this?

01:54:18.054 --> 01:54:19.248
Gold coins?

01:54:28.531 --> 01:54:29.862
Gold.

01:54:32.301 --> 01:54:34.531
Gold.

01:54:37.940 --> 01:54:40.204
You should have told me.

01:54:41.110 --> 01:54:43.237
How else would l know?

01:54:45.748 --> 01:54:47.739
Please don't be angry, my queen bee.

01:54:54.657 --> 01:54:57.922
-- l need to talk to you.
-- About what?

01:54:58.761 --> 01:55:01.389
l don't want you to stay here any longer.

01:55:01.497 --> 01:55:03.590
Things have taken a serious turn.

01:55:03.699 --> 01:55:06.327
Your presence may make matters worse.

01:55:07.436 --> 01:55:09.802
l want you to leave Sukhsayar
by tomorrow morning.

01:55:11.941 --> 01:55:14.637
Am l supposed to take orders from you?

01:55:14.744 --> 01:55:16.211
lt's not that.

01:55:17.613 --> 01:55:20.480
lf you leave for Calcutta,
it will be good for you,

01:55:21.384 --> 01:55:22.851
and for Sukhsayar as well.

01:55:24.086 --> 01:55:27.544
-- l have no work to do in Calcutta.
-- All the more reason to go.

01:55:28.591 --> 01:55:31.151
You've done too much work here.

01:55:32.962 --> 01:55:35.760
Don't think l haven't been
informed of your activities.

01:55:36.599 --> 01:55:39.534
From setting fire to the peasants' barns
to sinking Mirjan's boat,

01:55:40.503 --> 01:55:43.097
l've been informed of everything.

01:55:44.373 --> 01:55:47.206
You speak of unity
between Hindus and Muslims,

01:55:47.944 --> 01:55:50.879
but, in fact, you oppress Muslims.

01:55:52.381 --> 01:55:54.611
l won't tolerate it anymore.

01:55:56.953 --> 01:55:59.444
l may not believe in Swadeshi,

01:56:00.456 --> 01:56:03.118
but l truly admire
some Swadeshi leaders.

01:56:04.227 --> 01:56:09.529
But l don't admire those
whose actions belie their words.

01:56:10.766 --> 01:56:13.360
You're not saving the country.
You're ruining it.

01:56:14.604 --> 01:56:17.573
l won't allow this to go on in my estate.

01:56:17.673 --> 01:56:21.302
There's only one person here
l'm prepared to obey.

01:56:23.579 --> 01:56:25.410
Queen bee...

01:56:25.915 --> 01:56:29.180
Do you want me to stay or not?

01:56:38.027 --> 01:56:39.551
Queen bee.

01:56:40.596 --> 01:56:42.894
l'm waiting for your answer.

01:56:44.533 --> 01:56:47.366
Do you want me to leave?

01:56:50.006 --> 01:56:51.974
Please tell me, queen bee.

01:56:53.509 --> 01:56:55.443
l've said what l came to say.

01:56:58.047 --> 01:57:00.413
l hope l won't have to repeat it.

01:57:05.021 --> 01:57:06.852
Queen bee.

01:57:09.125 --> 01:57:11.252
What's the matter with you?

01:57:14.997 --> 01:57:17.898
You suddenly --
-- ls Amulya in your room?

01:57:18.000 --> 01:57:19.865
-- Amulya?
-- Yes.

01:57:19.969 --> 01:57:20.993
Why?

01:57:21.103 --> 01:57:24.004
Send him to me. lt's urgent.

01:57:24.707 --> 01:57:27.335
Can't you tell me why?

01:57:27.643 --> 01:57:29.702
No, l'll tell Amulya.

01:57:29.812 --> 01:57:31.780
Please send him to me.

01:57:31.881 --> 01:57:33.940
lt's my request.

01:57:35.151 --> 01:57:36.880
Very well.

01:59:13.516 --> 01:59:14.915
Amulya?

01:59:16.353 --> 01:59:19.550
Can you do me a favor?
-- Of course. What is it?

01:59:19.656 --> 01:59:20.953
Go to Calcutta.

01:59:21.058 --> 01:59:23.856
You can take the morning train
and return in the evening.

01:59:23.960 --> 01:59:26.087
The money for the journey is in this box.

01:59:26.196 --> 01:59:29.256
-- What's this box?
-- lt's my jewelry box.

01:59:29.366 --> 01:59:33.029
l need 5,000 rupees. Sell some
of my jewelry and bring me the money.

01:59:33.136 --> 01:59:35.229
l don't need any jewelry.
l can get you the money.

01:59:35.338 --> 01:59:36.669
How?

01:59:36.773 --> 01:59:39.708
This is not a small amount
we're talking about.

01:59:39.810 --> 01:59:41.175
l'll get it.

01:59:41.278 --> 01:59:43.405
No, do as l tell you.

01:59:44.014 --> 01:59:46.983
But why did you give
Mr. Sandip 5,000 rupees?

01:59:47.084 --> 01:59:48.949
He said he needed that much.

01:59:49.052 --> 01:59:52.749
No, according to our calculations,
we only needed 3,500.

01:59:52.856 --> 01:59:55.256
lf you give him more,
he spends it on himself.

01:59:56.026 --> 01:59:59.826
He's quite a spender.
He always travels first--class.

02:00:00.931 --> 02:00:02.990
-- Sandip?
-- Yes, sister.

02:00:03.100 --> 02:00:06.968
He says hardship saps a leader's strength.

02:00:07.804 --> 02:00:11.069
Well, l can't take back
what l've already given.

02:00:11.174 --> 02:00:14.007
He might need it in the future.
You get me the 5,000.

02:00:14.611 --> 02:00:17.978
Put the box away.
l'll get you the money tonight.

02:00:18.081 --> 02:00:20.015
-- How?
-- From the treasury.

02:00:21.017 --> 02:00:24.316
Are you insane?
What about the guards?

02:00:24.421 --> 02:00:26.446
We carry weapons, sister.

02:00:34.397 --> 02:00:36.558
Good heavens!

02:00:37.267 --> 02:00:39.326
Why are you upset, sister?

02:00:39.436 --> 02:00:41.529
We need funding
to carry out our work for the nation.

02:00:42.873 --> 02:00:44.841
Doesn't it bother you that you're stealing?

02:00:44.941 --> 02:00:46.841
Why?
Whose money is it?

02:00:46.943 --> 02:00:49.810
Mine today,
the moneylender's tomorrow.

02:00:49.913 --> 02:00:53.542
Why not use it for the cause?
-- No, Amulya.

02:00:53.650 --> 02:00:57.950
lf you go robbing treasuries,
l'll die of fear.

02:00:58.054 --> 02:01:00.318
Listen, you may not need
to sell all the jewelry.

02:01:00.423 --> 02:01:04.450
Sell as much as you need to
and bring back the rest.

02:01:05.462 --> 02:01:08.363
Take the box and carry it safely.

02:01:08.465 --> 02:01:11.366
And be careful, for heaven's sake.

02:01:12.302 --> 02:01:13.769
Very well, sister.

02:01:17.674 --> 02:01:20.040
l'll take my leave.
-- Okay.

02:01:44.067 --> 02:01:45.830
<i>Queen bee.</i>

02:01:55.512 --> 02:01:57.241
Are you leaving?

02:01:57.347 --> 02:01:59.611
ls there any reason for me to stay?

02:01:59.716 --> 02:02:01.707
Why do you say that?

02:02:01.818 --> 02:02:04.446
Can't you hear the note of discord?

02:02:05.488 --> 02:02:08.821
lf l've done anything wrong,
please forgive me.

02:02:08.925 --> 02:02:10.893
Don't leave like this.

02:02:11.428 --> 02:02:16.127
My husband said, ''The less one
knows you, the better one likes you''.

02:02:16.800 --> 02:02:19.564
Perhaps l know you too well.

02:02:19.669 --> 02:02:21.569
Don't say that, queen bee.

02:02:22.005 --> 02:02:24.735
Has knowing me meant nothing to you?

02:02:25.008 --> 02:02:26.908
Has it all been in vain?

02:02:27.010 --> 02:02:30.207
l believed you would
succeed in your endeavor.

02:02:30.313 --> 02:02:32.213
l wanted you to.

02:02:32.315 --> 02:02:34.579
But not anymore?

02:03:00.644 --> 02:03:03.238
<i>AIIah is great!</i>

02:03:57.334 --> 02:03:59.302
Kasim?

02:04:06.242 --> 02:04:07.709
Hands up.

02:04:10.580 --> 02:04:12.104
Hands up.

02:04:14.417 --> 02:04:15.611
Go inside.

02:04:15.719 --> 02:04:16.879
Go inside!

02:04:23.426 --> 02:04:24.620
Move.

02:04:27.097 --> 02:04:28.530
Turn around.

02:04:29.432 --> 02:04:31.024
Turn!

02:04:35.004 --> 02:04:36.938
Now open the safe.

02:04:37.607 --> 02:04:39.074
Open it!

02:04:44.114 --> 02:04:47.242
Take out 3,500 rupees.

02:04:48.017 --> 02:04:51.350
What's going on?
What's all the commotion?

02:04:51.621 --> 02:04:53.714
ls there a problem?

02:04:55.024 --> 02:04:56.753
l don't know.

02:04:57.427 --> 02:04:59.019
l hope it's not a riot.

02:04:59.129 --> 02:05:01.120
What are you saying?

02:05:01.464 --> 02:05:04.627
What will happen to us
if there's a riot here?

02:05:06.169 --> 02:05:08.364
We're going to Calcutta tomorrow.

02:05:09.205 --> 02:05:10.832
lt's no longer safe here.

02:05:10.940 --> 02:05:13.738
Who is ''we''?
Am l not coming with you?

02:05:16.513 --> 02:05:18.413
Did l say that?

02:05:20.517 --> 02:05:22.382
l'm so relieved.

02:05:22.485 --> 02:05:24.612
A treasury was looted nearby.

02:05:24.721 --> 02:05:27.588
What's to stop them from looting this place?

02:05:27.690 --> 02:05:31.353
lf they kill me, they'll burn my body
by that shriveled banyan tree.

02:05:31.461 --> 02:05:33.019
That would be awful.

02:05:34.964 --> 02:05:36.761
Go and get ready.

02:05:36.866 --> 02:05:38.697
Pack your things.

02:05:40.437 --> 02:05:42.701
You're serious about leaving, aren't you?

02:05:43.306 --> 02:05:45.331
l'm always serious.

02:05:46.376 --> 02:05:48.344
Don't you know me by now?

02:06:12.635 --> 02:06:14.330
Bimala?

02:06:17.140 --> 02:06:19.108
l have to tell you something.

02:06:19.209 --> 02:06:20.801
What is it?

02:06:21.077 --> 02:06:25.537
There were 5,000 rupees
in gold coins in two bags in the safe.

02:06:25.815 --> 02:06:27.749
l gave them to Sandip.

02:06:28.351 --> 02:06:30.285
He needed the money.

02:06:31.087 --> 02:06:34.989
Now you know how hard
it is to refuse him.

02:06:35.091 --> 02:06:36.490
l'll pay the money back.

02:06:36.993 --> 02:06:38.858
l gave Amulya my jewelry box.

02:06:38.962 --> 02:06:41.021
He'll sell my jewels and bring the money.

02:06:46.736 --> 02:06:51.935
l felt bad speaking to Sandip
like that in front of you.

02:06:54.377 --> 02:06:56.470
But l had to, Bimala.

02:06:57.480 --> 02:06:58.845
Things have taken a bad turn.

02:07:03.853 --> 02:07:06.788
lt's no longer safe for him to work here.

02:07:07.724 --> 02:07:10.249
But what about you?

02:07:13.963 --> 02:07:16.727
Your safety is what concerns me.

02:07:17.133 --> 02:07:20.728
No one else matters to me anymore.

02:07:21.538 --> 02:07:24.735
Tomorrow, we're going to Calcutta.

02:07:25.308 --> 02:07:27.037
All three of us.

02:07:28.077 --> 02:07:30.602
And if something happens before then?

02:07:33.050 --> 02:07:34.608
You won't leave the house, will you?

02:07:37.721 --> 02:07:41.248
lf something happens,
l'll have to go and intervene, Bimala.

02:07:46.063 --> 02:07:47.621
l knew it.

02:07:50.000 --> 02:07:53.231
l knew l'd be punished.

02:07:54.337 --> 02:07:56.771
l'll be punished.

02:07:59.943 --> 02:08:01.808
Punished? Why, Bimala?

02:08:02.679 --> 02:08:05.239
You haven't done anything wrong.

02:08:06.783 --> 02:08:11.652
l don't even have the right
to ask you for forgiveness.

02:08:13.890 --> 02:08:17.417
But you've come back to me,
haven't you?

02:08:18.662 --> 02:08:20.960
Haven't you, Bimala?

02:08:29.206 --> 02:08:33.905
lt seems like ages since l last
looked at you and spoke to you.

02:08:35.879 --> 02:08:37.972
What came over me?

02:08:38.715 --> 02:08:41.240
Why did this happen?

02:08:43.086 --> 02:08:44.883
You've done nothing wrong, Bimala.

02:08:45.922 --> 02:08:49.255
For ten years, you never saw
another man besides me.

02:08:51.161 --> 02:08:53.152
Don't forget that.

02:09:25.228 --> 02:09:27.423
There's 3,500 rupees here.

02:09:28.331 --> 02:09:31.562
Please return the jewelry box
and the gold coins.

02:09:32.836 --> 02:09:36.169
Where did you get that money?
Where have you been?

02:09:37.073 --> 02:09:39.064
To the treasury.

02:09:40.177 --> 02:09:41.405
l hope nobody saw you.

02:09:49.653 --> 02:09:51.518
l had my face covered.

02:09:51.855 --> 02:09:54.790
Did you see any trouble in the village?
-- There's a riot.

02:09:56.893 --> 02:10:00.090
The Muslims have broken
into the temple of Visalakshi.

02:10:10.574 --> 02:10:12.337
Are you leaving?

02:10:13.944 --> 02:10:15.571
Yes. To Rangpur.

02:10:20.917 --> 02:10:22.111
Will you come with me?

02:10:35.799 --> 02:10:37.198
l must go now.

02:10:45.475 --> 02:10:47.102
Hail Motherland.

02:11:03.660 --> 02:11:05.218
What are you thinking?

02:11:06.463 --> 02:11:08.124
Nothing.

02:11:09.799 --> 02:11:12.267
l don't want to think.

02:11:13.470 --> 02:11:15.563
l want to forget.

02:11:17.140 --> 02:11:20.303
Everything that's happened
in the last few days.

02:11:20.777 --> 02:11:23.678
Forget? But why?

02:11:23.780 --> 02:11:24.542
Nikhil!

02:11:28.084 --> 02:11:30.075
Come in, Sandip.

02:11:33.256 --> 02:11:35.486
This is the age of breaking rules.

02:11:36.226 --> 02:11:38.421
Your wife came out of her confinement,

02:11:38.528 --> 02:11:40.428
and now l've invaded
the privacy of your bedroom.

02:11:40.530 --> 02:11:42.464
l hope you'll forgive me.

02:11:44.934 --> 02:11:49.030
These are your property,
which l duly return.

02:11:49.806 --> 02:11:52.673
One jewelry box
and two bags of gold coins.

02:11:53.677 --> 02:11:55.144
The jewelry box?

02:11:55.912 --> 02:11:59.678
Your devotee didn't take it with him,
but he brought me the money.

02:12:03.086 --> 02:12:08.023
Since you have your valuables, l hope
you won't mind me keeping the money.

02:12:08.124 --> 02:12:10.422
-- Are you leaving?
-- Yes, Nikhil.

02:12:11.394 --> 02:12:14.022
The train to Rangpur leaves in an hour.

02:12:16.232 --> 02:12:19.531
Do you hear that?
The riots have started.

02:12:19.636 --> 02:12:21.365
Amulya saw them.

02:12:21.671 --> 02:12:26.267
And now l must make
my proverbial escape.

02:12:26.576 --> 02:12:27.907
l must live.

02:12:28.678 --> 02:12:30.908
l have a lot of work left to do.

02:12:31.181 --> 02:12:33.706
Don't make the same mistake again.

02:12:33.817 --> 02:12:36.081
Can't you see the results of your actions?

02:12:37.053 --> 02:12:39.248
l follow the <i>Bhagavadgita,</i> Nikhil.

02:12:39.522 --> 02:12:43.458
l am concerned only
with the action, not the result.

02:12:43.560 --> 02:12:47.860
And l consider Ravana to be
the hero of Ramayana, not Rama.

02:12:47.964 --> 02:12:50.899
So l can't accept advice
from the followers of Rama.

02:12:52.035 --> 02:12:53.935
The easy road isn't for me, Nikhil.

02:12:55.605 --> 02:12:57.300
l'll take my leave.

02:13:02.679 --> 02:13:04.772
This will stay with me.

02:13:10.086 --> 02:13:12.077
l'm keeping this as a memento.

02:13:13.089 --> 02:13:15.421
Who knows if we'll ever meet again?

02:13:18.194 --> 02:13:19.491
Good--bye, Nikhil.

02:13:24.200 --> 02:13:25.758
Queen bee.

02:13:31.841 --> 02:13:34.139
Hail Motherland.

02:14:09.313 --> 02:14:11.213
Courage, Bimala.

02:14:12.716 --> 02:14:16.277
l must go out to them now.
-- No! l won't let you!

02:14:16.386 --> 02:14:17.751
l must.

02:14:20.390 --> 02:14:22.153
Please don't stop me.

02:14:23.593 --> 02:14:25.151
My dear.

02:14:56.493 --> 02:14:59.394
-- You let him go?
-- We tried to stop him.

02:14:59.446 --> 02:15:01.141
He wouldn't listen to us!

02:15:02.482 --> 02:15:04.279
You witch!

02:15:04.985 --> 02:15:08.921
You sent him to his death!

02:15:09.556 --> 02:15:13.788
Have you no pity
in your heart of stone?
